Document: FontVariation
Path: godot/classes/class_fontvariation.rst
Summary: Provides OpenType variations, simulated bold/slant, and additional font settings like OpenType features and extra spacing.

FontVariation provides OpenType variations, simulated bold/slant, and additional font settings like OpenType features and extra spacing.

To use simulated bold font variant:
GDScript:
    var fv = FontVariation.new()
    fv.base_font = load("res://BarlowCondensed-Regular.ttf")
    fv.variation_embolden = 1.2
    $Label.add_theme_font_override("font", fv)
    $Label.add_theme_font_size_override("font_size", 64)
C#:
    var fv = new FontVariation();
    fv.SetBaseFont(ResourceLoader.Load<FontFile>("res://BarlowCondensed-Regular.ttf"));
    fv.SetVariationEmbolden(1.2);
    GetNode("Label").AddThemeFontOverride("font", fv);
    GetNode("Label").AddThemeFontSizeOverride("font_size", 64);

To set the coordinate of multiple variation axes:
GDScript:
    var fv = FontVariation.new();
    var ts = TextServerManager.get_primary_interface()
    fv.base_font = load("res://BarlowCondensed-Regular.ttf")
    fv.variation_opentype = { ts.name_to_tag("wght"): 900, ts.name_to_tag("custom_hght"): 900 }
---CHUNK---
Document: FontVariation
Path: godot/classes/class_fontvariation.rst
Summary: List of properties for the FontVariation class, including font settings, spacing, and OpenType features.

Properties:
- base_font (Font): The base font used for this variation. Default: null.
- baseline_offset (float): The baseline offset of the font. Default: 0.0.
- opentype_features (Dictionary): A dictionary of OpenType feature tags and their values. Default: {}.
- palette_custom_colors (PackedColorArray): Custom colors for the font palette. Default: PackedColorArray().
- palette_index (int): The index of the font palette to use. Default: 0.
- spacing_bottom (int): Extra spacing added to the bottom of the glyphs. Default: 0.
- spacing_glyph (int): Extra spacing added between glyphs. Default: 0.
- spacing_space (int): Extra spacing added to the space character. Default: 0.
- spacing_top (int): Extra spacing added to the top of the glyphs. Default: 0.
- variation_embolden (float): The embolden strength of the font. Default: 0.0.
- variation_face_index (int): The face index of the font variation. Default: 0.
- variation_opentype (Dictionary): A dictionary of OpenType variation axis tags and their values. Default: {}.
- variation_transform (Transform2D): The transformation applied to the font glyphs. Default: Transform2D(1, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0).
---CHUNK---
